1. Create account on docker hub
2. https://docs.docker.com/get-started/workshop/02_our_app/ use the code and same docker file to build an image
3. tag the image with <your docker hub account name>/<imagename>:<tag>
4. run docker login 
5. run docker push <your image name> 


